ROUNDCUBE PLUS QUOTE PLUGIN
===========================

This plugin displays inspirational quotes from famous people on the mail page sidebar.

REQUIREMENTS
------------
- Roundcube: 1.5, 1.6
- PHP: 7.4 or higher

INSTALLATION
------------
1. Copy the directories xquote and xframework included in this package to the 'plugins' directory of your Roundcube
   installation.

2. Edit the file <roundcube>/config/config.inc.php, add xquote to the plugins array and specify your license key.

For more information on installing Roundcube Plus plugins see:
https://roundcubeplus.com/helpdesk/knowledgebase.php?article=29

The users will be able to remove the quotes from the sidebar by unchecking "Show Daily Quote" in the Sidebar section
of the Settings page.

COMPATIBILITY / LIMITATIONS
---------------------------
This plugin has been created for the standard version of Roundcube as provided on the Roundcube website:
https://roundcube.net. It might not work properly with customized versions of Roundcube including the version
provided as part of the Kolab system. Please note that we cannot provide any technical support for the plugin
deployed on a non-standard version of Roundcube.

